# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Research material & copyrighted game assets — NEVER commit these.
# This folder holds the original game, the SaintsX fan patch, and third-party
# reference code, included on this machine for study only. Keeping it out of
# version control is both a legal requirement (we do not redistribute game
# files) and a clean-room hygiene measure (the distributed engine must not
# embed reference-derived code or assets).
